{"type": "article", "id": 45742, "title": "奥迪“小丑”广告很有趣，WPP 考虑退出明年戛纳广告节 | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人相关的一切", "date": "2017-09-30T04:14:55Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 1928, "name": "AR"}, {"id": 1298, "name": "福特"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 26306, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 62, "image": "img/article/article_show/201709301124400tUOWElo1Cx23hai.jpg", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">值得一提的案例</h3><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 14.0px 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: #393939} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 14.0px 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: #393939; min-height: 19.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 14.0px 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: #393939; -webkit-text-stroke: #393939} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 14.0px 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: #393939; -webkit-text-stroke: #393939; min-height: 19.0px} p.p5 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 10.0px 'Heiti SC Light'; color: #323333; -webkit-text-stroke: #323333} p.p6 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'Songti SC'; color: #323333; -webkit-text-stroke: #323333} p.p7 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 14.0px 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: #393939; -webkit-text-stroke: #323333; min-height: 19.0px} p.p8 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 14.0px 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: #393939; -webkit-text-stroke: #323333} p.p9 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 28.0px 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: #484545; -webkit-text-stroke: #484545} p.p10 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 14.0px 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: #393939; -webkit-text-stroke: #484545} p.p11 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 14.0px 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: #393939; -webkit-text-stroke: #484545; min-height: 19.0px} p.p12 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'Songti SC'; color: #d41e18; -webkit-text-stroke: #d41e18} p.p13 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'Songti SC'; color: #323333; -webkit-text-stroke: #323333; min-height: 25.0px} p.p14 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 10.0px 0.0px; line-height: 56.0px; font: 48.0px 'Helvetica Neue'; color: #323333; -webkit-text-stroke: #323333} p.p15 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 10.0px 0.0px; line-height: 56.0px; font: 48.0px 'Heiti SC Light'; color: #323333; -webkit-text-stroke: #323333} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font-kerning: none; color: #545454; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #545454} span.s3 {font-kerning: none; color: #dd4b39; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #dd4b39} span.s4 {font: 10.0px Arial; font-kerning: none; color: #dd4b39; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #dd4b39} span.s5 {font: 18.0px Georgia; font-kerning: none} span.s6 {font: 18.0px 'Songti SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s7 {font: 18.0px 'Songti SC'; font-kerning: none; color: #323333} span.s8 {font-kerning: none; color: #323333; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #323333} span.s9 {font: 48.0px 'Heiti SC Light'; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p><a href=\"http://creative.adquan.com/show/42296\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>地球上唯一一个禁止女性驾驶的国家沙特阿拉伯解禁</b></a>，尼桑、大众、福特等汽车商开启了庆祝营销。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170930112601GU5RrVv83LWOd6Tb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.003333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p>尼桑-阿拉伯语“2018”和“女孩”</p></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201709301134272nxSwJfjHTvuzlD7.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.896629\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">福特的后视窗广告</figcaption></figure></div><p><a href=\"http://www.madisonboom.com/2017/09/29/audi-campaign/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>奥迪拍了支喜剧广告</b></a>，讲的是一群小丑开巴士的历险旅程，意思是有了奥迪的智能驾驶技术，就算车技再差也平安无事。</p><p class=\"\">本次作品的创意来自 BBH London。此前奥迪也曾推出“拳击”创意、音乐会创意演奏等表现形式，用来展现奥迪车身带有的智能科技。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=y055615n36s&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.madisonboom.com/2017/09/29/hundreds-of-wildebeest-commercials-are-coming-again-this-time-telling-women-about-elastic-aesthetics/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>百雀羚为新品推出新主题概念—弹性美学，</b></a>共包含四支广告，演绎了四个女性们在生活中熟悉的场景：恋爱关系篇、闺蜜关系篇、剩女标签篇、社交问题篇。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=h0554shu2bl&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p><a href=\"http://www.adweek.com/agencies/telepathic-bulldog-talks-a-man-out-of-a-stupid-decision-in-this-new-spot-for-bulldog-skincare-for-men/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>英国专注男士天然护肤第一品牌 Bulldog 推出全新的品牌形象</b></a>——一只有心灵感应能力的斗牛犬。这支斗牛犬不仅通过和男主人公谈心，阻止了失魂落魄企图抢银行的男主，还给了他护肤意见。adam&amp;eveDDB 作为创意公司拍摄了这支广告。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170930113116zC9MBL4JquVai57A.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.547619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>最后，也挺重要</h3><p><a href=\"http://www.adweek.com/agencies/wpp-tightens-the-screws-on-cannes-lions-owner-amid-threats-to-skip-next-years-festival/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>继阳狮集团之后，WPP 集团明年也有可能退出戛纳创意节。</b></a>来自 WPP 集团内部邮件显示，WPP 集团向戛纳国际创意节（Cannes Lions）和欧洲创意大奖（Eurobest）的母公司 Ascential 提出特殊要求。如果后者无法满足这些要求，那么 WPP 集团也可能像阳狮集团那样退出其相关奖项及活动。苏铭天爵士和 WPP 高管会在十月与 Ascential 首席执行官 Duncan Painter 当面讨论相关事宜。<br></p><p class=\"\">目前 WPP 集团已明确全面退出专注欧洲市场的奖项赛事 Eurobest。</p><p><a href=\"http://www.adweek.com/digital/buoyed-by-the-success-of-the-dancing-hot-dog-snapchat-is-opening-up-3d-ar-ads-for-the-real-world/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Snapchat 开放了3-D AR 广告，希望为广告客户创造更多基于实用的广告形式。</b></a>首批客户包括 Bud Light 和华纳兄弟。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170930114317QK1OneSCotgYTzDf.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.606250\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">Bud Light 设计了一个虚拟的啤酒供应商形象，在真实街头兜售冰啤酒；而华纳兄弟公司则创造了一部会飞的汽车（类似于《哈利波特》里韦斯莱先生那辆）。<br></p><p class=\"\">题图来源：<a href=\"https://always4evernow.wordpress.com/tag/ad/\" rel=\"nofollow\">always4evernow</a></p>"}